abstract: Soccer Roundup; New York Red Bulls and Toronto FC play to 1-1 draw, but Toronto is officially eliminated from postseason contention; other soccer results noted.
snippet: Thierry Henry scored in the 88th minute to give the New York Red Bulls their 16th draw in 31 games.
lead_paragraph: Thierry Henry scored in the 88th minute to give the New York Red Bulls their 16th draw in 31 games.
